<h2 class="wp-block-heading list-start">Chest And Shoulder Anatomy</h2>



<p>Understanding the anatomy of your chest and shoulders is key to maximizing your workouts. Let&#8217;s break it down into manageable insights.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>The Chest: More Than Just Muscle</strong></h3>



<p>The chest is not just for aesthetics; it&#8217;s a powerhouse of strength and functionality. Here&#8217;s how its main components contribute:</p>


